1. high Availability
Systems are available for a long period of time.
2. Scalability
Increase workload on the currnet resources.
3. Elasticity
Increase workload on additional resources.
4. Agility
Quickly respond to changes.
5. Disaster Recovery

IaaS = Infrastructure as a serivice
PaaS = Platform as a serivice
SaaS = Software as a serivice
